
(1) Install the Node.js JavaScript runtime environment using your OS package manager.


(2) Verify that Node.js has been installed:

    $ node -v

    v0.10.25


(3) Verify that NPM has also been installed as a dependency of Node.js:

    $ npm -v

    1.3.10


(4) Install the Webpack module bundler:

    $ npm install webpack

    ...


(5) Install the Babel transpiler:

    $ npm install babel-loader

    ...


(6) Install the Babel preset 'es2015':

    $ npm install babel-preset-es2015

    ...


(7) Install the Babel preset 'react':

    $ npm install babel-preset-react

    ...


(8) Bundle / transpile the JavaScript with Webpack for deployment:

    $ ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack.js --config ./webpack.config.js

    ...

